  PREAMBLE
===============================================================================

This License ("License") governs the use, reproduction, modification, and
distribution of the Neuro compiler, toolchain, and associated materials
("the Software"). It is designed to achieve three goals simultaneously:

  1. OPEN CONTRIBUTION: Any individual or organization may study, modify,
     and contribute to the Software. The contribution path is frictionless.

  2. ECOSYSTEM FREEDOM: Programs written in the Neuro language and compiled
     by the Neuro compiler are wholly exempt from this License and may be
     used, distributed, and sold under any terms the author chooses.

  3. INTEGRITY PROTECTION: During the critical pre-stabilization phase,
     protections against commercial re-packaging of the compiler itself,
     competitive AI reproduction, and misleading fragmentation are in effect.

